node.text:
Define your home décor!

We are in love with these rugs by @trustedknots which are giving us the luxury we have been looking for with its unique designs. Steal a discount of Upto 70% to add a style statement to your rooms.

Head over to the website link in bio or swipe up to our story to find out more about these handwoven rugs.

Alternatively, you can give them a call on +1 (929) 437-6707 to discuss more about their amazing collection.
